{"tid":1346640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇事黑警，有事警察？入黎睇睇醫生同黑警分別","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:52:06.000Z","uid":14262,"like":967,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"57913822a6df98a857293c18809fe75bae3d42ee","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCqmMpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCqmMpV.png&h=4323382a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察職責係保護香港市民<br />\n更何況警察唔係單單收份人工先要履行職責<br />\n世界各地警察都一樣，唔係單單一份職業<br />\n係一種使命，維持社會安寧，保護市民生命財產。<br />\n<br />\n但香港警察及藍絲<br />\n荒謬地說出''無事黑警，有事警察''而及''咁叻唔好搵警察''<br />\n如果當年，醫生跟你們一樣思維，沙士會變成點？<br />\n<br />\n以上圖係轉發只陳沛然醫生"},{"pid":"17de44d085d48d821f9b204e378c7b399ffb4c76","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00925e3a5e5e342fa4412ebe9f4c0f9d319a848a","tid":1346640,"uid":258927,"like":181,"dislike":0,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ya93fjo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYa93fjo.png&h=566c6752&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43075f87d28025d391879e55aecded9c703789c7","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"香港警察，面係自己丟光"},{"pid":"b71c71bb2de6cf4423c7ae0c9030a0dda8f8ea12","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2478eeb48ee147bbd4dae4ea3ee60e3cb5e11ad3","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手推多啲比人睇！<br />\n我真係見到藍絲既言論就好撚嬲"},{"pid":"b16bca75c2d992f9616d81e0fac8a6fe6126584f","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"我自己推"},{"pid":"6cc9508f5824b428a4d6