<br />\n已經有二萬三千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be2f8739ca2dc5509f0cc2d1eeef54529be57fd","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"求求文宣組幫手重整，再發放比所有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6504db76748a59205439aeac59bd16276d10c83","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"我知好多仲細，未經歷過沙士時期，<br />\n但班仆街藍絲一定感受過<br />\n<br />\n我想文宣組幫手，目標有兩個，<br />\n1. 好多話唔識點拆<br />\n2. 比班藍絲、警察睇睇自己既歪理，同當年醫生既分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求求文宣組幫手重整，再發放比所有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e5de65360d793e955491a0cfc79a36cacb9ed3","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"求求文宣組幫手重整，再發放比所有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d2d8520290760dda4dd191601bcf5e4ca2e409","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54