n有人組緊，我好願意參與，保護市民，雖然我只係個Gym撚，但都盡我所能"},{"pid":"473af7fc37454391e3eb5371afaa20e547c58f4b","tid":1346640,"uid":7502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"醫學院畢業同毅進畢業嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed050bc96069748e856dc04e86e800eae327fd68","tid":1346640,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9431222241ab5817fba232e53e10257d5567ab79","tid":1346640,"uid":210835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57913822a6df98a857293c18809fe75bae3d42ee","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCqmMpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCqmMpV.png&h=4323382a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察職責係保護香港市民<br />\n更何況警察唔係單單收份人工先要履行職責<br />\n世界各地警察都一樣，唔係單單一份職業<br />\n係一種使命，維持社會安寧，保護市民生命財產。<br />\n<br />\n但香港警察及藍絲<br />\n荒謬地說出''無事黑警，有事警察''而及''咁叻唔好搵警察''<br />\n如果當年，醫生跟你們一樣思維，沙士會變成點？<br />\n<br />\n以上圖係轉發只陳沛然醫生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"尖子同毅進既分別"},{"pid":"19c41fdac1a2980f84c628a4b2dd8d2e538d872d","tid":1346640,"uid":78612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"咪撚再講埋啲有事警察無事黑警既on9嘢<br />\n<br />\n黑警係香港唯一擁有合法武力同執法權力既紀律部隊，唔係我想搵你，係有事必須搵你，一係你班黑警自己宣布放棄武力同執法權力，下放比市民，我咪唔撚搵你囉"},{"pid":"7522902cf578ec764adc12dfb5ef17f3af044cfc","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7ac1b17990698d1cf7ecfb8a32a5773693641e3","tid":1346640,"uid":252854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8de2ca450de22df65c108406fe5892bb26c8760e","tid":1346640,"uid":172190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"警察係香港至高無尚既職業<br />\n<br />\n先不論佢濫權，不盡責，同黑社會聯繫拍膊頭，過份武力等等，佢地仲有一個特權叫休班特權。<br />\n<br />\n佢地休左班講乜殺示威者打示威者挑釁仇恨冇後果。但佢地又唔比有休班老師休班醫生，一講良心說話發表己見，班特權警察就追住黎咬唔放過，痴撚柒線。"},{"pid":"d301297ace9073a9c83330d8b92ad10de3420bc1","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06ff82b2d637b3e659f0a094cec4249bf64a8214","tid":1346640,"uid":24466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"陳醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c324afd6cde7610b296d04a567029a45790b39","tid":1346640,"uid":220360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba8682a4c27352870a0bd26813d176395fe910b3","tid":1346640,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"[文宣]推到全世界都知香港有幾威<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4335bbc9170280b6542d2ecdba854f8d4f0aaa7","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09a440d5b67eedfa345b262c42a06eb62b4566e8","tid":1346640,"uid":279051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca5978f25e2250c7c24ec830c1eee376e00e88e5","tid":1346640,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"香港警察<br />\n請交低配槍，你地唔配有"},{"pid":"2c454786b991cd57461fa0f039f0764b629487cc","tid":1346640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10152ba214c1190a64e98b318d3417f70125766f","tid":1346640,"uid":247266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa8bfe731b435d159f1c6d3a075cfd177c265ef7","tid":1346640,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep